text: Étienne-François-Louis-Honoré Letourneur, Le Tourneur, or Le Tourneur de la Manche (15 March 1751 – 4 October 1817) was a French lawyer, soldier, and politician of the French Revolution. Category:1751 births Category:1817 deaths Category:People from Manche Category:French politicians
title: Étienne-François Le Tourneur
